## To be Detailed:
    - Systems have Reviewers and Contributors
    - Squads pickup Initiatives to contribute to and work across all systems they need to enhance or build
    - Squads are reviewed for necessary skills and training to contribute to the Initiatives they pickup
    - Members of the squad may also be reviewers of systems they are not contributing to under the current Initiatives they are not part of
    - Systems are owned by Architects and Reviewers, whereas the Squads are managed by the Tech Leads and Engineering Managers